parameters:
\nc<>What is this place?! Why is there a hidden place inside the
sewer?!

\nc<>Be careful, Levantia. There's an incredible evil aura
overflowing.
\nc<>(That's right. Just breathing alone makes my head throb.)

\nc<>The malevolent energy is flowing out from that crack over
there. What on earth could be inside...?

\nc<>That black thing... is it the mysterious power that Lilith
used in the previous battle...?

\nc<>What should we do, Levantia? If we leave it like this, the
mother body will absorb that power and recover!

\nc<>(Is it just my imagination? It seems like the power is not
being absorbed by the mother body, but rather, the power is
trying to engulf the mother body...)

\nc<>I see. You brought me here to make it easier for them,
huh?

\nc<>Huh, what do you mean? You can understand the words of the
Invasoid now?
\nc<>No? I just guessed based on the atmosphere.

\nc<>Regardless of the facts, we should do the same thing,
right? We can't just leave that mother body as it is.
\nc<>That's true. That power is clearly abnormal.
\nc<>Thank you for guiding me this far.
\nc<>I'll make it as easy as possible for you, okay?
\nc<>I obtained the memory T4: Invasoid Baby.

\nc<>Good listeners increased by 7,000, while bad listeners
increased by 3,000.
